data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This meticulously cared-for 3 bedroom, 3 bath gem boasts numerous upgrades and breathtaking panoramic views of Glassford Hill & the Bradshaw Mountains right from your front porch. Step into a freshly painted interior that radiates warmth and charm. Wooden shutter window treatments add a touch of elegance throughout the home. Custom stone molding at the base of the flooring adds a distinctive look to every room. The great room features a stone fireplace and mantle, perfect for cozy evenings with loved ones. The primary bedroom offers a large walk-in closet featuring a wardrobe storage system. The ensuite boasts a dual vanity, upgraded walk-in shower with snail entry, and floor-to-ceiling stone tile. The split floorplan offers two additional bedrooms
